{"word":"περιπήγνυμι","slug":"περιπήγνυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περιπήγνυμι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πήξω</el>) </el><p/><i>to fix round, to make a fence round</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> loci, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>περιπέπηγα</el>, <i>to be fixed around</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>τὰ ὑποδήματα π.</el> <i>are frozen on the feet</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}